{"tid":1548354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家D POST可唔可以唔好不停騎劫","createTime":"2019-09-07T03:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T04:48:39.000Z","uid":54517,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"52e29046435f82298dc6f34b9a65b4e72160db04","tid":1548354,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:54:25.000Z","msg":"知文宣好重要,但係都唔好不停騎劫其他POST,以家攪到資訊好混亂,入一個POST拉落去幾個唔關事嘅文宣,基本上幫唔到件事,反而會另到大家有資訊疲勞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「資訊疲勞綜合症」(Information Fatique Syndrome, IFS) 是發生在我們過多暴露於媒體、技術和資訊下的產物，在這個社會十分普遍。我們的大腦無法跟上所有接收的訊息，處於擾人的手機和無線網路電磁場中讓人頭痛和筋疲力竭，進而犯錯並做出錯誤的決定.</strong></span>"},{"pid":"6f68c725629ceb087d8c095587dad31422f9818a","tid":1548354,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:55:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2136201d20bca1f0ca5dec508dd43e50c7db93","tid":1548354,"uid":261530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f94f6d8a592168a70a70002e20cae23ebcde379","tid":1548354,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:56:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c1701fb4cbae26e420c7eafd7debf8b9e718af","tid":1548354,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:57:00.000Z","msg":"先十連"},{"pid":"301c1c2b9d6dd0c342f3e75f8c399f13a85d64a7","tid":1548354,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:57:12.000Z","msg":"10<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf6c70bdfd17641752f8f4081fd1e256a0aadfc","tid":1548354,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim